{"tid":1537544,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英外相促港設獨立委員會 調查警員鎮壓示威行動","createTime":"2019-09-04T03:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T03:44:35.000Z","uid":68738,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"02d124fefaa376cb235873a274d68195f1c6779b","tid":1537544,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190903/large/1567522004_3cbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190903%2Flarge%2F1567522004_3cbc.jpg&h=e3d1eea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藍韜文呼籲成立獨立調查委員會(路透社)<br />\n<br />\n香港警方鎮壓反送中示威人士的「最低武力水平」一直惹來許多抨擊，不少人士都先後要求特首林鄭月娥成立獨立調查委員會調查，但林鄭都未有回應訴求。英國外相藍韜文周二亦呼籲港府成立獨立委員會，進行可靠、獨立調查香港警方鎮壓示威者的行為。<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文在國會發言時說︰「關於警員的行為以及他們鎮壓示威的手法是否超出正常水平及反應過度，很明顯應該成立一個獨立警察投訴委員會進行調查，但大前提是必須可信。」<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190903/60006919?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190903%2F60006919%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3IE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=3dffd0e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190903%2F60006919%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=7e290c48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190903/60006919?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"f0495cbd404e49cffaff9b7171d9fb97a55284c2","tid":1537544,